Package: SpaColExt
Type: Package
Title: Infer spatial colonization and extinction dates
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Clara Casabona i Amat & Simon Bouchard
Maintainer: Clara Casabona i Amat  <Clara.Casabona.I.Amat@USherbrooke.ca>
Description: Package to infer spatial colonization and extinction dates of species
    Use bayesian approach to estimate the probability of species extant using a modified version of Solow 1992 and 2014 functions at a different spatial levels.
    This is a package in development that should be inprove in the next year.
